# Project Context: survey-builder

You are working on `survey-builder`, an MVP web application for building, publishing, and analyzing surveys with Supabase.

## Current stage and goals
- Stage: MVP for live demo.
- Core flow: create surveys, publish links, collect responses, analyze results.
- Keep existing auth and survey list stable while building creator + sharing.

## Project defaults
- i18n-first across all user-facing features.
- Prefer performance-aware implementations.
- Keep code clean, consistent, and easy to review.
